{"id":68497,"date":[{"year":1939,"month":4,"day":16}],"page":"11","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"儿童团","column":"诗歌","genre":"文学作品","count":"159","ytitle":"","mtitle":"我的爸妈","ftitle":"","authors":["思秋"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"思秋"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我的爸爸:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是一个神圣的铁匠。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自从敌人轰毁了他的工厂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他便跑到了抗敌的后方。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他会修理飞机和大礮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他会铸造大刀和长枪。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"永远的，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他永远要这样尽他的力量。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我的妈妈:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是一个勤俭的农妇。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自从敌人闯进了她的乡土，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她便投入了抗战的队伍。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她在军营里担任烹饪缝补，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她会做受伤健儿的看护。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"永远的，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她永远要这样替祖国服务。"}]}